Tomorrow
Wednesday, February 27, 2019 - A friend shows up to save the day and you are tickled pink to see them. You surround yourself with so many types of people, it is inevitable that you would rub shoulders with a bona fide superhero. However, if you wish to join their team, you may have to hustle to get yourself into gear. Beyond capes and crowns, the real question is one of resources. You might need to dig deeper than you initially thought to drum up the goods to support your new adventure. Although there are perks to being linked with this dynamo of positivity, you still must make your own choices. Never forget your power comes from within.
